snippet.textDisplay:
Dear Ashley,

I’m posting this here cause this is your latest video, and I WANT YOU TO TAKE A BREAK ON NEW YEAR. Take the time off and ready your ass for the tiring process of moving, you’re gonna need it. I would just like to thank
you, for making my 2019 not as shitty thanks to your videos. Ever since I subscribed (this is gonna sound like bullshit but) I felt so much better about myself, I saw a difference and felt like I glowed up (which we shouldn’t expect on everyone, you’re all beautiful with or without one), I felt more confident with my fashion sense, I stepped out of my comfort zone and people actually appreciated my outfits. Thank you for helping me better, and more comfortable, and confident, and thanks for putting your time and effort to be able to make really good quality videos for your subscribers, we appreciate it, and we would also appreciate it if You know when you have to rest, do not waste your energy trying to feel better on putting up a video every week, especially if you aren’t feeling well. Hope that you’ll be happy in your new apartment soon, and that you’ll be happy living in your new home. We’re here to support you all the way through, and hope that the next year will not be as shitty! Sending lots of love to you and to everyone else that subscribed to this lovely human being!



Love,
From a loving subscriber❤️


P.s. this letter was long and confusing, just know that I love and appreciate all that you do for us!!
